title: How to Make Vegetable Spring Rolls Recipe 春卷, CiCi Li
description:
Spring rolls are popular traditional Chinese snacks. Back in the days, people eat spring rolls on the Li Chun Day, which is at the beginning of spring. In order to pray for good health, and they call it “bite the spring.” Later spring rolls gradually become an everyday snack.  Today let’s learn to make Vegetable Spring Rolls.
